            "draft_value": "* Robotic exploration of the solar system and Earth's climate to answer fundamental scientific questions\n* Local impact via $4.5M+ in recent grants to the University of Rhode Island and $176k to Providence College for planetary modeling\n* Strategic defense of U.S. space leadership against China's rapid expansion into lunar and Martian exploration\n* Economic multiplier effect supporting precision measurement software at Hexagon Manufacturing Intelligence in North Kingstown",
